summary: Adds deadly Breton assassin and former member of the Dark Brotherhood,  Sabine Joubert.
descriptionHtml:
Silent and unseen, Sabine is one of Skyrims most notorious assassins and never misses her mark.  Out of the Dark Brotherhood and working for herself,  she has decided fighting alongside the Dragonborn is a worthy cause! Skilled with a bow and dual wielding.

She can be found at the Winking Skeever.

Requirements

XPMSE 

HDT physics 

UNP based body

Recommended 

[url=https://www.loverslab.com/topic/27618-blacktalon-armor-for-unp/]Blacktalon armor[/url]﻿

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3871/]Weapons of the Third Era [/url]﻿

Thanks to all the excellent mod Authors of Skyrim Nexus, the incredible talent in the Image Gallery and especially,  my friends at the Art Fletcher Discord server who helped assist me with troubleshooting :) love you guys!
